  "summaries": [
    "The <b>Volcano</b> (<b>Fiery Greatsword</b> on <linked>[img:Old-gen console version]</linked><linked> Old-gen console</linked> and <linked>3DS</linked><linked>[img:Nintendo 3DS version]</linked>) is a <linked>broadsword</linked> crafted from <linked>Hellstone Bars</linked>. It lacks <linked>autoswing</linked> and has a slow swing speed, but it has the second-longest reach and second-highest damage of all swords in <linked>pre-Hardmode</linked>. It has a <span class=\"chance\"><s>50*</s>1/2 (50%)</span> chance to inflict the <linked>On Fire!</linked> <linked>debuff</linked> for 3 seconds and emits fiery light particles when swung.",
    "On the <linked>[img:Desktop version]</linked><linked> Desktop version</linked>, <linked>[img:Console version]</linked><linked> Console version</linked>, and <linked>[img:Mobile version]</linked><linked> Mobile version</linked>, it creates an explosion upon hitting an enemy, dealing 75% base damage (30 base damage) to the enemy and all targets in an area around the enemy, and has a 100% chance to inflict On Fire! for 3 seconds. Each explosion creates a tall plume of fire and smoke particles.",
    "The Volcano is one of the key ingredients in crafting the <linked>Night's Edge</linked>.",
    "Its best <linked>modifier</linked> is <b>Legendary</b>."
